Noonim.

107
00:08:35,490 --> 00:08:38,910
You scared me. You're back early. Did you get done early?

108
00:08:38,910 --> 00:08:41,550
- Noonim. 
 - What?

109
00:08:41,550 --> 00:08:43,460
