110
00:08:43,460 --> 00:08:44,800
Fast news.

111
00:08:44,800 --> 00:08:47,030
Did you really dump him?

112
00:08:47,030 --> 00:08:50,250
- I didn't really— 
 - Who did you kiss?

113
00:08:50,250 --> 00:08:52,070
How do you know that?

114
00:08:52,070 --> 00:08:54,350
How long has it been and he's already talking?

115
00:08:54,350 --> 00:08:56,220
How long has it been?

116
