Did you do it recently?

120
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:08,770
Do you just kiss all the time?

121
00:09:08,770 --> 00:09:11,570
What is your charm?

122
00:09:11,570 --> 00:09:13,720
Who did you do it with? When did you do it?

123
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:17,680
You did it with #2, right? I'm right! You did it with #2.

124
00:09:20,790 --> 00:09:22,950
Noona, Ji Na Noonim recently with a guy—

125
00:09:22,950 --> 00:09:25,080
Don't listen to him.

126
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:27,480
They are getting married.

127
00:09:28,750 --> 00:09:31,820
Well, it's not like we're doing it...

128
00:09:31,820 --> 00:09:33,270
It happened to be like this.

129
00:09:33,270 --> 00:09:35,250
No.

130
00:09:35,250 --> 00:09:36,320
It's true.

131
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:39,490
I think it's true.

132
00:09:42,160 --> 00:09:44,620
- We need to talk. 
 - We need to talk.

133
00:09:44,620 --> 00:09:47,560
Wait...

134
00:09:54,340 --> 00:09:56,930
Is that why I haven't been able to see you lately?

135
00:09:59,220 --> 00:10:04,290
Rather than not being able to see, it was more like you didn't know me.

136
00:10:04,290 --> 00:10:08,420
Of course, I didn't know you were thinking that far.

137
00:10:11,920 --> 00:10:16,660
Brother, you're really a big person.

138
00:10:16,660 --> 00:10:19,950
