139
00:10:22,110 --> 00:10:26,220
Honestly, it's not an easy decision.

140
00:10:26,220 --> 00:10:29,830
I don't feel all comfortable.

141
00:10:32,450 --> 00:10:38,880
I've been carrying this for the moment like this.

142
00:10:38,880 --> 00:10:41,620
I've been saving up ever since I was 20 years old, doing part-time.

143
00:10:41,620 --> 00:10:44,300
Why are you giving that to me?

144
00:10:44,300 --> 00:10:47,530
I've been carrying this all the time wondering

145
00:10:47,530 --> 00:10:50,150
