146
00:10:52,260 --> 00:10:54,690
I think this is the right time.

147
00:10:54,690 --> 00:10:57,630
You should use it for the marriage.

148
00:10:57,630 --> 00:11:01,050

149
00:11:03,630 --> 00:11:09,120
