156
00:11:45,840 --> 00:11:47,720
Please stay by...

157
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:51,440
my sister, Brother.

158
00:11:58,760 --> 00:12:00,450
You will do that, right?

159
00:12:07,310 --> 00:12:08,750
Yes.

160
00:12:31,850 --> 00:12:35,630
Marriage? You're getting married?

161
00:12:36,620 --> 00:12:38,830
I think that's what he wants to do.

162
00:12:42,930 --> 00:12:44,370
How about you?

163
00:12:45,060 --> 00:12:46,750
That's not what you want?

164
00:12:47,370 --> 00:12:51,180
I want to do everything that he wants to do.

165
00:12:52,940 --> 00:12:57,170
Hey, marriage is not something you do out of loyalty.

166
00:12:57,170 --> 00:12:59,350
No matter how much you love him—

167
00:13:01,300 --> 00:13:03,030
Unnie.

168
00:13:05,350 --> 00:13:06,910
Hey.

169
00:13:08,300 --> 00:13:11,680
No matter what you do, I will check everything before you get married.

170
00:13:11,680 --> 00:13:13,750
What do I do?

171
00:13:18,460 --> 00:13:20,140
Are you crying?

172
00:13:20,140 --> 00:13:22,520
No matter how much I try to end it,

173
00:13:22,520 --> 00:13:26,790
no matter how much I try to run away, I end up at the same place.

174
00:13:27,790 --> 00:13:29,910
I try to abandon, but I can't.

175
00:13:29,910 --> 00:13:34,080
I try to forget, but I can't. What do I do?

176
00:13:38,100 --> 00:13:41,520
I don't have time, but I also don't have any other ways.

177
00:13:41,520 --> 00:13:43,640
What do I do?

178
00:13:45,710 --> 00:13:46,820
Dong Kyeong.

179
00:13:46,820 --> 00:13:48,870
It's all my fault.

180
00:13:50,200 --> 00:13:52,590
It's just all my fault.

181
00:13:53,980 --> 00:13:56,980
No, it's not your fault.

182
00:13:56,980 --> 00:13:59,480
You didn't do anything wrong.

183
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:02,030
So do everything that you want to do.

184
00:14:02,030 --> 00:14:04,540
I don't care what.

185
00:14:04,540 --> 00:14:08,680
Forget everything I said earlier.

186
00:14:08,680 --> 00:14:12,970
If you're happy now, that's all that matters to me.

187
00:14:12,970 --> 00:14:15,640
So don't say that you don't have time.

188
00:14:17,690 --> 00:14:19,590
Don't say such things.

189
00:14:32,710 --> 00:14:36,930
