190
00:14:38,720 --> 00:14:41,880
Unnie...

191
00:16:02,880 --> 00:16:05,000
Leave them. I'll do it.

192
00:16:23,980 --> 00:16:26,220
Being here, now I get it.

193
00:16:27,530 --> 00:16:28,620
Get what?

194
00:16:28,620 --> 00:16:31,480
That you've been waiting for me like this.

195
00:16:31,480 --> 00:16:34,830
I wondered what you did sitting here, not going in your room.

196
00:16:34,830 --> 00:16:38,070
You always waited for me to finish everything.

197
00:16:39,310 --> 00:16:41,050
It's nothing like that.

198
00:16:45,430 --> 00:16:47,950
You can stop looking after me.

199
00:16:52,010 --> 00:16:54,500
You can stop waiting for me.

200
00:17:10,640 --> 00:17:12,140
You raised me well.

201
00:17:12,140 --> 00:17:15,360
- Lee Hyeon Kyu. 
 - I want to stop bothering you now.

202
00:17:15,360 --> 00:17:17,690
I really need to grow up.

203
00:17:17,690 --> 00:17:20,090
If you keep taking my back,

204
00:17:20,090 --> 00:17:22,540
I keep wanting to lean on you.

205
00:17:23,250 --> 00:17:27,080
See? I'm blaming you again.

206
00:17:32,240 --> 00:17:34,100
Are you saying you're moving out?

207
00:17:34,100 --> 00:17:35,500
Yes.

208
00:17:36,550 --> 00:17:38,210
I'm going into the world.

209
00:18:13,180 --> 00:18:15,590
