210
00:18:16,910 --> 00:18:18,450
Still...

211
00:18:21,890 --> 00:18:23,810
I should go now.

212
00:18:39,520 --> 00:18:41,260
So...

213
00:18:41,260 --> 00:18:43,730
- Doctor. 
 - I heard.

214
00:18:43,730 --> 00:18:45,960
You're getting married.

215
00:18:45,960 --> 00:18:47,210
When did you hear that?

216
00:18:47,210 --> 00:18:50,920
