217
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:52,950
Congratulations.

218
00:18:53,690 --> 00:18:55,690
Sure.

219
00:18:55,690 --> 00:18:59,310
That's why I'm saying this.

220
00:18:59,310 --> 00:19:00,890
So...

221
00:19:00,890 --> 00:19:03,330
You...

222
00:19:03,330 --> 00:19:05,630
don't want to do the biopsy?

223
00:19:08,840 --> 00:19:14,160
You said it's in a dangerous spot.

224
00:19:18,950 --> 00:19:21,090
Then let's do this.

225
00:19:22,500 --> 00:19:27,260
Just until your wedding. Let's just postpone it till then.

226
00:19:28,260 --> 00:19:29,640
Okay.

227
00:19:30,660 --> 00:19:33,210
To be honest, you're right.

228
00:19:33,210 --> 00:19:35,290
It's very dangerous.

229
00:19:35,290 --> 00:19:38,960
We might open up then just close it without being able to do anything.

230
00:19:38,960 --> 00:19:44,400
That's why I wanted to proceed with the treatment with just the biopsy and not a surgery.

231
00:19:44,400 --> 00:19:46,260
But...

232
00:19:47,590 --> 00:19:49,840
to live a little longer,

233
00:19:51,160 --> 00:19:53,650
to live a little longer

234
00:19:53,650 --> 00:19:56,570
and to be a little happier,

235
00:19:56,570 --> 00:19:58,820
we decided on this treatment.

236
00:20:01,020 --> 00:20:02,750
Right.

237
00:20:04,780 --> 00:20:07,160
But you'll have to rush the wedding.

238
00:20:07,160 --> 00:20:11,320
If there's something wrong, come to the hospital immediately. You can promise that, right?

239
00:20:11,320 --> 00:20:13,430
Thank you.

240
00:20:14,380 --> 00:20:17,180
Don't be too scared, though.

241
00:20:17,180 --> 00:20:20,970
You're doing great right now.

242
00:20:20,970 --> 00:20:22,980
I'll make sure to attend your wedding.

243
00:20:22,980 --> 00:20:25,060
When are you planning to do it?

244
00:20:26,480 --> 00:20:30,610
Well, I'm not sure yet.

245
00:20:36,390 --> 00:20:38,500
My sister is going to be discharged.

246
00:20:42,020 --> 00:20:44,350
What does your aunt say?

247
00:20:45,330 --> 00:20:47,100
She's worried.

248
00:20:49,360 --> 00:20:51,260
Tell her to not worry.

249
00:20:51,260 --> 00:20:53,700
I'll take all the responsibility.

250
00:20:53,700 --> 00:20:57,370
I'll take her and bring her back.

251
00:20:58,060 --> 00:21:00,100
So tell her to not worry

252
00:21:00,100 --> 00:21:03,250
and let's do everything that Dong Kyeong wants to do.

253
00:21:04,130 --> 00:21:06,140
What's going on?

254
00:21:06,140 --> 00:21:08,920
I thought you'd be furious and oppose everything.

255
00:21:11,560 --> 00:21:15,190
She was bawling.

256
00:21:18,960 --> 00:21:22,250
She pretends to be okay but she's probably not okay.

257
00:21:22,250 --> 00:21:24,230
She must be anxious about everything.

258
00:21:26,760 --> 00:21:30,800
I don't even want to think about it.

259
00:21:32,190 --> 00:21:35,170
But just so there are no regrets.

260
00:21:35,890 --> 00:21:37,790
Let's do everything.

261
00:21:41,450 --> 00:21:42,800
Okay.

262
00:21:47,340 --> 00:21:48,790

263
00:21:54,340 --> 00:21:56,490

264
00:21:58,670 --> 00:22:00,190
Yes.

265
00:22:00,190 --> 00:22:01,900
 Let's meet.

266
00:22:03,130 --> 00:22:06,110
Okay. Where?

267
00:22:06,970 --> 00:22:08,850
Okay.

268
00:22:12,490 --> 00:22:14,200
I got to go.

269
00:22:14,200 --> 00:22:16,020
Noonim.

270
00:22:16,020 --> 00:22:17,430
Yeah?

271
00:22:19,620 --> 00:22:22,040
Do well so you don't regret anything.

272
00:22:22,800 --> 00:22:25,010
Worry about yourself!

273
00:22:26,180 --> 00:22:28,040
Bye.

274
00:22:59,360 --> 00:23:01,030
Is it marriage blues?

275
00:23:01,030 --> 00:23:04,040
Does marrying me make you that anxious?

276
