00:48:50,940 --> 00:48:53,020
they will end up dying.

548
00:49:12,090 --> 00:49:14,350
This is a secret, but...

549
00:49:14,350 --> 00:49:17,300
there are words that will never disappear.

550
00:49:18,160 --> 00:49:20,110
Around twelve.

551
00:49:20,110 --> 00:49:22,630
In there, your name is included.

552
00:49:22,630 --> 00:49:24,380
Dong Kyeong (deep longing).

553
00:49:27,050 --> 00:49:28,910
How about Sa Ram (person)?

554
00:49:29,630 --> 00:49:31,430
That's included as well.

555
00:49:46,450 --> 00:49:48,880
It's so annoying.

556
00:49:48,880 --> 00:49:50,690
Why?

557
00:49:50,690 --> 00:49:53,590
I don't want to sleep, but I'm tired.

558
00:49:54,970 --> 00:49:58,860
Sleep. You're a person, so you need to sleep.

559
00:50:03,060 --> 00:50:07,730
I will sleep for just a moment. Seriously, just a moment.

560
00:50:07,730 --> 00:50:09,150
Okay.

561
00:50:14,440 --> 00:50:17,060
Don't go anywhere.

562
00:50:17,060 --> 00:50:18,530
Okay.

563
00:50:19,150 --> 00:50:22,070
Stay right next to me.

564
00:50:22,070 --> 00:50:23,460
Okay.

565
00:50:25,260 --> 00:50:27,620
Don't disappear.

566
00:51:11,630 --> 00:51:13,850
Is this the last day?

567
00:51:14,880 --> 00:51:17,030
I came here to say goodbye.

568
00:51:17,570 --> 00:51:20,570
I'm the one who came to say goodbye.

569
00:51:21,380 --> 00:51:23,750
You knew, right?

570
00:51:27,900 --> 00:51:30,630
That I will make this kind of decision.

571
00:51:34,770 --> 00:51:37,870
God... knows everything.

572
00:51:37,870 --> 00:51:40,280
No matter what, nothing is set in stone.

573
00:51:40,280 --> 00:51:42,390
Even if she wished for doom,

574
00:51:42,390 --> 00:51:45,420
I cannot know if that is possible or not.

575
00:51:47,270 --> 00:51:49,360
So how about if you just

576
00:51:49,360 --> 00:51:50,940
place your bet on that?

577
00:51:50,940 --> 00:51:54,000
No, I am going to place my bet on something I know for sure.

578
00:51:54,000 --> 00:51:58,320
The method that will surely save her.

579
00:51:58,320 --> 00:52:00,480
Why did you make that kind of pointless promise?

580
00:52:00,480 --> 00:52:03,350
I must've had to keep that promise.

581
00:52:03,350 --> 00:52:05,820
- Keep what? 
 - Whether it's the promise,

582
00:52:05,820 --> 00:52:09,410
or her, or this world.

583
00:52:14,850 --> 00:52:17,730
You have more things to protect than me.

584
00:52:28,320 --> 00:52:31,280
I plan on living a bit longer.

585
00:52:31,280 --> 00:52:34,410
While depending on the heart of a human,

586
00:52:34,410 --> 00:52:37,110
I want to continue on this life for a little bit longer.

587
00:52:38,390 --> 00:52:42,400
Isn't this... your first time?

588
00:52:42,400 --> 00:52:44,520
That you're thinking of that?

589
00:52:44,520 --> 00:52:45,920
Yeah.

590
00:52:47,580 --> 00:52:51,040
Someday, that heart will stop again.

591
00:52:53,620 --> 00:52:56,620
But there are many things I want to see in this body.

592
00:52:57,360 --> 00:53:01,420
I really like this life. For many reasons.

593
00:53:01,420 --> 00:53:03,860
What do you want to see?

594
00:53:03,860 --> 00:53:05,330
Flowers.

595
00:53:05,890 --> 00:53:08,050
Fully blooming flowers.

596
00:53:25,220 --> 00:53:27,160
Where did you go?

597
00:53:27,160 --> 00:53:31,430
- Oh, just for a moment— 
 - Where were you?

598
00:53:35,740 --> 00:53:37,570
I'm sorry.

599
00:53:37,570 --> 00:53:39,950
I thought you just left.

600
00:53:39,950 --> 00:53:42,270
I thought you disappeared.

601
00:53:42,270 --> 00:53:46,100
When I opened my eyes and you weren't there, I seriously–

602
00:53:46,100 --> 00:53:49,150
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

603
00:53:49,150 --> 00:53:52,620
I just closed my eyes for a bit and opened them, and I thought

604
00:53:52,620 --> 00:53:56,030
did a day pass already? Did two days pass?

605
00:53:56,030 --> 00:53:59,910
Is it all over? That's what I thought!

606
00:53:59,910 --> 00:54:02,500
I don't have any time...

607
00:54:02,500 --> 00:54:06,370
I really don't have much time left.

608
00:54:06,370 --> 00:54:09,330
It's okay. I'm still here.

609
00:54:09,330 --> 00:54:13,310
We still have one day.

610
00:54:17,430 --> 00:54:20,020
I don't think I can do this.

611
00:54:20,840 --> 00:54:22,780
I tried not to,

612
00:54:22,780 --> 00:54:26,330
and I don't want to do that either, but–

613
00:54:26,330 --> 00:54:27,920
Do what?

614
00:54:29,980 --> 00:54:33,040
Can you wish for me to not love anyone?

615
00:54:33,040 --> 00:54:34,870
Not anyone.

616
00:54:35,830 --> 00:54:37,690
That's my wish.

617
00:54:41,970 --> 00:54:43,550
I can't do that.

618
00:54:43,550 --> 00:54:45,400
I told you it's my wish!

619
00:54:45,400 --> 00:54:48,860
That was under our contract! Why can't I do that?

620
00:54:48,860 --> 00:54:50,410
Because I need to save you.

621
00:54:50,410 --> 00:54:52,920
If I survive because of that,

622
00:54:52,920 --> 00:54:56,580
everything is meaningless!

623
00:54:56,580 --> 00:54:59,840
It is meaningful. To me.

624
00:55:01,560 --> 00:55:03,560
After losing you,

625
00:55:03,560 --> 00:55:06,160
after losing everyone you love,

626
00:55:06,160 --> 00:55:10,110
in that empty world, I may have to live for eternity.

627
00:55:14,760 --> 00:55:16,540
Dong Kyeong.

628
00:55:24,350 --> 00:55:26,170
Humans...

629
00:55:28,870 --> 00:55:31,890
Humans can love again.

630
00:55:31,890 --> 00:55:34,540
No...

631
00:55:34,540 --> 00:55:36,570
Because they are humans.

632
00:55:37,420 --> 00:55:40,720
You can overcome that. I can't.

633
00:55:42,050 --> 00:55:43,880
You know, right?

634
00:55:43,880 --> 00:55:47,380
I don't eat, sleep, or cry.

635
00:55:47,380 --> 00:55:49,500
I don't feel sympathy or love.

636
00:55:51,390 --> 00:55:54,040
But you are human.

637
00:55:54,040 --> 00:55:56,020
So you can.

638
00:55:57,220 --> 00:56:00,890
I can't. Without you,

639
00:56:00,890 --> 00:56:03,990
I seriously can't...

640
00:56:10,130 --> 00:56:13,340
Don't be like that. Don't say that.

641
00:56:13,340 --> 00:56:17,940
I did wrong. I did wrong, so–

642
00:56:24,130 --> 00:56:27,390
I did wrong!

643
00:56:49,390 --> 00:56:52,280
I have a real wish.

644
00:56:58,030 --> 00:57:00,710
I want you to take me to

645
00:57:00,710 --> 00:57:02,810
the doomed world.

646
00:57:05,700 --> 00:57:07,960
That's impossible.

647
00:57:07,960 --> 00:57:11,990
I'm not asking you to actually take me there.

648
00:57:12,780 --> 00:57:15,470
It's fine if it's just a lie.

649
00:57:15,470 --> 00:57:19,220
Even if it's just a dream or imagination.

650
00:57:19,220 --> 00:57:21,320
Just for one day,

651
00:57:22,320 --> 00:57:25,980
I want to be with you for one last day there.

652
00:57:28,560 --> 00:57:30,570
Grant me this wish.

653
00:57:31,590 --> 00:57:34,210
This is really my wish.

654
00:58:06,780 --> 00:58:07,900
So here...

655
00:58:07,900 --> 00:58:10,090
This is the doomed world.

656
00:59:05,690 --> 00:59:08,040
Seriously, no one is–

657
00:59:09,800 --> 00:59:12,440
My voice sounds way too loud.

658
00:59:12,440 --> 00:59:14,950
Since there is no sound here.

659
00:59:18,360 --> 00:59:20,760
It's so strange.

660
00:59:22,220 --> 00:59:24,780
It will be lonely.

661
00:59:24,780 --> 00:59:29,660
In this doomed world, I am no longer Doom.

662
00:59:32,580 --> 00:59:34,690
I am nothing.

663
00:59:46,330 --> 00:59:49,860
The fact that I have a responsibility in everything that disappears means

664
00:59:49,860 --> 00:59:55,490
because of everything that disappears, I can exist.

665
00:59:56,400 --> 00:59:59,680
In this world where nothing is left to disappear,

666
01:00:01,010 --> 01:00:07,410
I am... just like suspended dust.

667
01:00:14,490 --> 01:00:17,680
So that's why I'm saying it's meaningless.

668
01:00:17,680 --> 01:00:20,370
My existence without you.

669
01:00:25,310 --> 01:00:27,420
It looks lonely.

670
01:00:29,030 --> 01:00:32,370
Your face watching things that disappear.

671
01:00:33,230 --> 01:00:38,250
Even still, it looks lonely.

672
01:00:39,250 --> 01:00:41,090
Same for you.

673
01:00:42,320 --> 01:00:44,410
They're always lonely.

674
01:00:45,210 --> 01:00:47,390
Your eyes watching me.

675
01:00:57,760 --> 01:01:00,340
I have somewhere I want to go to.

676
01:01:21,600 --> 01:01:23,520
Why here?

677
01:01:23,520 --> 01:01:25,370
I want to pray.

678
01:01:25,370 --> 01:01:28,020
There is no God in a doomed world.

679
01:01:29,410 --> 01:01:31,900
Since there are no humans?

680
01:01:31,900 --> 01:01:33,540
Yeah.

681
01:01:33,540 --> 01:01:36,120
But I'm here.

682
01:01:36,120 --> 01:01:39,940
In this world, the human,

683
01:01:39,940 --> 01:01:42,130
I'm here.

684
01:02:32,360 --> 01:02:35,980
Night still comes in a doomed world...

685
01:02:37,480 --> 01:02:41,990
At the cathedral earlier, what did you pray for?

686
01:02:43,360 --> 01:02:44,920
It's a secret between me and God.

687
01:02:44,920 --> 01:02:47,150
You said God doesn't exist in this world.

688
01:02:47,150 --> 01:02:50,590
The moment you wished for one, God may have been born.

689
01:02:54,770 --> 01:02:57,180
What did you pray for?

690
01:02:57,180 --> 01:02:59,170
I...

691
01:03:01,040 --> 01:03:07,940
I just... wished for the last time that I will not love anyone.

692
01:03:09,490 --> 01:03:14,460
I know. It's a wish and a prayer that will not come true.

693
01:03:14,460 --> 01:03:16,900
But I still gave it a try.

694
01:03:29,230 --> 01:03:30,320
Dong Kyeong...

695
01:03:30,320 --> 01:03:32,400
I love you.

696
01:03:37,080 --> 01:03:40,420
In the end, the person I loved the most is you.

697
01:03:41,560 --> 01:03:45,390
I'm sorry. For loving you.

698
01:03:46,970 --> 01:03:49,950
For loving you the most, I'm sorry.

699
01:03:51,800 --> 01:03:53,710
Thank you.

700
01:03:55,180 --> 01:03:57,290
For loving me.

701
01:04:15,720 --> 01:04:22,980
♫  In the distant future, you and I...  ♫

702
01:04:22,980 --> 01:04:29,960
♫  The seasons we'll be living face to face  ♫

703
01:04:29,960 --> 01:04:36,740
♫  The countless emotions  ♫

704
01:04:37,880 --> 01:04:43,870
♫  I just want to be with you  ♫

705
01:04:48,080 --> 01:04:50,950
♫  Only you  ♫

706
01:05:00,410 --> 01:05:02,830
It's almost 12 o'clock.

707
01:05:11,120 --> 01:05:13,580
It's okay.

708
01:05:13,580 --> 01:05:15,790
Everything is okay.

709
01:05:38,400 --> 01:05:42,230
I wanted to be with you until the very last moment.

710
01:05:42,910 --> 01:05:44,810
I know.

711
01:05:47,620 --> 01:05:49,690
I love you...

712
01:05:51,370 --> 01:05:53,190
I know.

713
01:05:55,160 --> 01:05:57,750
I'm so scared.

714
01:05:59,400 --> 01:06:02,350
- Dong Kyeong— 
 - Don't say anything.

715
01:06:03,780 --> 01:06:05,790
Don't say... anything.

716
01:06:05,790 --> 01:06:08,310
This contract is void.

717
01:06:08,310 --> 01:06:10,220
No.

718
01:06:10,940 --> 01:06:12,330
No.

719
01:06:12,330 --> 01:06:17,340
Your sadness and pain, I will take them all.

720
01:06:17,340 --> 01:06:21,430
Don't worry. I will take them all.

721
01:06:21,430 --> 01:06:23,530
No, you can't.

722
01:06:25,470 --> 01:06:27,580
I don't want you to.

723
01:06:30,390 --> 01:06:33,950
I was created for you.

724
01:06:33,950 --> 01:06:36,500
So don't cry.

725
01:06:36,500 --> 01:06:38,820
Live happily.

726
01:06:40,420 --> 01:06:45,340
I was born to do that. To make you happy.

727
01:06:45,340 --> 01:06:48,090
Can you not leave?

728
01:06:50,150 --> 01:06:52,700
Seriously, can you not?

729
01:06:54,400 --> 01:06:57,200
The wish I made at the cathedral earlier.

730
01:06:59,530 --> 01:07:01,620
I wished for your happiness.

731
01:07:01,620 --> 01:07:04,920
Then you have to be here.

732
01:07:06,010 --> 01:07:09,190
You have to be here.

733
01:07:11,870 --> 01:07:15,110
Do you remember what I told you last time?

734
01:07:15,110 --> 01:07:19,440
Even if it rains, even if you're the only one without an umbrella, it's not a big deal.

735
01:07:20,320 --> 01:07:23,180
If you run, you'll reach home quickly.

736
01:07:27,090 --> 01:07:29,720
Even if I disappear, run.

737
01:07:31,260 --> 01:07:33,590
Don't look back and run.

738
01:07:33,590 --> 01:07:36,000
Then you will quickly...

739
01:08:29,970 --> 01:08:37,020

740
01:08:38,680 --> 01:08:43,580
♫  I wanna be with you  ♫

741
01:08:43,580 --> 01:08:46,620
♫  At the end of a tiring day  ♫

742
01:08:46,620 --> 01:08:53,690
♫  Without a sound, come to me and hug me   ♫

743
01:08:53,690 --> 01:09:01,310
♫  Wait for me at the end of this road  ♫

744
01:09:01,310 --> 01:09:06,570

♫  My feelings for you can't be hidden  ♫

745
01:09:06,570 --> 01:09:09,290
 Did everything actually happen?

746
01:09:09,290 --> 01:09:16,320
 Did you really stay by my side?

747
01:09:16,320 --> 01:09:19,120
 - Do you not need anything? 
 - Hyung.

748
01:09:19,120 --> 01:09:21,990
 Unni, do you not call Cha Joo Ik?

749
01:09:22,930 --> 01:09:28,250
 Today, we all ate together and everyone said they miss you.

750
01:09:28,250 --> 01:09:33,620
 If I pass you by, like you always did, can you grab my hand?

751
01:09:35,560 --> 01:09:37,520
 You're happy, right?

752
01:09:37,520 --> 01:09:40,120
♫   ...shines because of you  ♫

753
01:09:40,120 --> 01:09:43,160
♫  Just you alone  ♫

754
01:09:43,160 --> 01:09:45,140
♫  Beyond this deepening sadness  ♫
